first_para: Neil Quentin Gordon Parish (born 26 May 1956) is a British Conservative Party politician. He was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Tiverton and Honiton, from 2010 to 2015, elected at the 2010 general election. He had been a Member of the European Parliament (MEP) for South West England from 1999 to 2009.
